snippet.title: PLAYGROUND 2 AUCTION | @CarryMinati @triggeredinsaan, Scout, Ashish & Harsh Beniwal
snippet.description:
Playground is back! CarryMinati, Triggered Insaan, Ashish, ScoutOP & Harsh are trying to find the best contestants for the real money auction & pick them for their teams for the season starting 30th January streaming LIVE on YT & on Amazon miniTV! 

Voting lines for Super Subs open on Rumble, closes at 4:30 PM on 30th January. Vote here https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.robosoft.playverseStage
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
*Auction rules*
‚Ä¢ 40 contestants
‚Ä¢ Only 28 will remain post auction
‚Ä¢ 20 players, selected through bidding, will go directly into teams 
‚Ä¢ 8 players will go into super subs
 ‚Ä¢ Of this, 5 players will be selected by the 5 mentors
 ‚Ä¢ And 3 players will be selected through voting on Rumble
‚Ä¢ Player mix for teams - 1 Pro-player, 1 international player, Min. 1 player from previous season, Min. 1 female player
‚Ä¢ Every week two players will get eliminated and new players will be selected from supers subs 
‚Ä¢ 25L purse of each mentor to bid for players
‚Ä¢ If a mentor has invoked an RTM card for a player during the Tryouts, they have the Right to Match the final bid on that player during the auction

Lyrics: 

Paye ni shaapa chhalle apa change aa kalle 
Jad rabb saddu tur jana apa kite aap ni challe 
Karte sab rabb havale aape kade vair ni kadde 
Gair ton aas nayi rakhi te apne kade pair ni shadde 
Dil de doctor ne ajj tayi aashiq da ilaaj ni kareya 
Kavaa ton kathe hoke kalla ik baaj ni mareya 
Ajj tayi kade raaj nayi kita jungle vich moran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Maade jo time ch chad gaye kise nal harkh nayi koi 
Koi sanu ki samje painda hun fark ni koi 
Koi lakh kar jaye maada mathe kade vatt ni paya 
Pandita nu future de layi main nayi kade hath dikhaya 
Sach ni koi hoya aisa jo akhan ne biyan ni kareya 
Hoya ni saadh koi aisa rabb da jine dhayan ni dhareya 
Jinna vich uddeya firda saadh pune diya loran ne 
Dabde nayi dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne


Dheethan nal dheeth bade aa aunde kise guage ch haini 
Kimat meri puch ona ton jina di main range ch haini 
Chadar ton bahar kade vi nek na pair pasare 
Bolan di lod ni sanu paundi aa chupp khilare 
Sade te asar nayi kareya oh allarhan diyaan toran ne 
Vekhe kayi khunje laate jhanjar deya shoran ne 
Allarha impress karan layi na kaddiya kade tohra ne 
Dabde ni dabbe ton malak hath dorran ne 
Jithe kamm kare halimi nayi karna joran ne

snippet.title: Sonam Wangchuk is fighting for Ladakh | Ladakh Protests Explained | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain why Sonam Wangchuk is protesting? What does Sonam Wangchuk and the rest of Ladakh wants from the government of India? And why Sonam Wangchuk was briefly under house arrest.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

Join us as we delve into the devastating impact of climate change on the beautiful region of Ladakh. From melting glaciers to changing weather patterns, this explainer video will highlight the current situation and its consequences on the local communities and their way of life. Watch now to understand how this remote corner of the world is affected and what can be done to mitigate the effects of global warming on Ladakh. #ClimateChange #Ladakh #sonamwangchuk

snippet.title: MAAN MERI JAAN SUPREMACY I KING AFTER-PARTY INDIA TOUR AFTERMOVIE TEASER
snippet.description:
#MaanMeriJaan #ChampagneTalk #King 

In October 2022, I presented my 3rd Studio Album Champagne Talk to the World. We also set out on a Tour across 18 cities the very next day to celebrate the album with you. 

Hyderabad-Pune-Indore-Mumbai-Vadodara-Ludhiana-Nagpur-Kolkata-Delhi-Jaipur-Ahmedabad-Bengaluru-Ranchi-Delhi-Kolkata-Guwahati-Surat-Goa
And the one song that roared across the nation was Maan Meri Jaan.

It‚Äôs not possible to put into words the Magic we experienced. You all came together to make my biggest dream come true. And to prove that Kingsclan is not just a word. It‚Äôs an emotion we all feel. Together. 

Thank you for the Phenomenon. Thank you for creating the Term of the year ‚Äì Maan Meri Jaan Supremacy. And thank you for being there. 

Special Thanks to Team Innovation for amazing Tour partners. 
TOUR AFTERMOVIE DROPS ON 5TH FEBRUARY. STAY TUNED

FEATURES :
Arpan Kumar Chandel aka King
Section 8 : Dj
Dan Thomas : Drums
Birraj K Taneja : Keys
Shubanshu Singh : Guitar
Danik Ghosh : Bass Guitar
Hanish Taneja : Sound Engineer & SFX
Additional Sound Team : Piyush 
Amey Pendarkar : Lights Engineer
Harsh Patel : Visual Engineer
Visuals : XO Visuals, Kartik Kher, Himanshu Baisoya, Deepit Badani, Mihir Shah, Vatsal Goswami
Tight Security : Security
Team Bluprint : Bhavya Anand, Dhruv Wadhwa, Ankit Mundotia, Chiranshu Thakur, Sweta Ojha, Kanav Kumar

Farq Episode 27 - [Eng Sub] - Faysal Quraishi - Sehar Khan - Adeel Chaudhry - 30th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Faysal Quraishi as Kamal Hassan
Sehar Khan as Irsa

Sohail Sameer as Rashid
Sabiha Hashmi as Husna Phuppo
Faiza Gillani as Yasmeen
Raeed Muhammad Alam as Jamshed
Aadi Khan as Mani
Farah Nadir as Razia

snippet.title: We Build Black Hole Making Machine -100% Real | Part-1
snippet.description:
Please Watch Part-2 Also. Everything You Will See In Part2 Is Real. NO Vfx or Graphics Are Used. Our Machine Will Create Something Which Looks Like Black Hole, Galaxy, Supernova, Universe etc.

A black hole is a region of spacetime where gravity is so strong that nothing, including light or other electromagnetic waves has enough energy to escape its event horizon. 

Our blackhole have also powerful gravity in the center and can pull a human size object inside the center.

#blackhole #mrindianhacker #science

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3681 - 30 Jan 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3681: Badey Guru Ji Ke Darshan
--------------------------------------------------------
Taarak finally finds the confidence to walk into his boss's cabin. When Taarak's boss notices that Taarak is sporting a green shirt, he snaps at him. Taarak tells his boss that while traveling there, he saw a clairvoyant who advised him to dress in green since it would be lucky for him to do so. Taarak's boss becomes irate with him for listening to someone else instead of his Guruji. Champaklal is brought inside his boss's cabin by Taarak in order to defend his statements. Champaklal turns out to be Taarak's enigmatic clairvoyant who suggested that he wear a green shirt. What happens next? Follow to learn more!

Show Name ‚Äì Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast ‚Äì  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Raj Anankat
Episodes No - 3681, 30 Jan 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #‡§§‡§æ‡§∞‡§ï‡§Æ‡•á‡§π‡§§‡§æ‡§ï‡§æ‡§â‡§≤‡•ç‡§ü‡§æ‡§ö‡§∂‡•ç‡§Æ‡§æ #sab

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in Gokuldham Co-operative Society and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. Jethalal lives in Gokuldham society and owns an electronics shop.  'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Raj Anankat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises.

*About* 
------------

Judwa behene Divya aur Drishti ko apne janam se mila hai shakti ka vardaan. Drishti bhavishya kaal ko dekh sakti hai aur Divya ussey badal sakti hai. Inke mata pita ne apni jaan ka balidaan dekar bachaya dono beheno ko par bichad gaye bachpan mai Divya aur Drishti. Alag alag parivaaron mai pale bade par ek doosre ko dhundhte rahe. 
Ek kaali shakti - Pishaachini haasil karna chahti hai sarva shaktishali Kaal Vijay Ratna ko aur saalon se padi hai dono beheno ke peeche. Dobara mil hi jaati hai Divya aur Drishti. Ek saath milkar karti hai muqaabla Pishaachini ka aur karte hai waada ussey khatam karne ka.

snippet.description:
"SYAAPA" is Himachal's First Ever web series produced by KANGRA BOYS

"SYAAPA" is the story of four friends and one of their senior advocate Makkhan. In this episode all four friends after being expelled from their college return to their ancestral house in their village. Here they encounter a dead body in their house and all of them are haunted by the fear that they might be accused of his murder. Now, they call one of their college senior advocate Makhan for help. Let's see how these four friends deal with this problem and if advocate Makkhan comes to help them.

Tere Bin Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

Tere Bin Episode 10 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 26th January 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab‚Äôs life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family‚Äôs decision regarding her and Murtasim‚Äôs life. Meerab‚Äôs hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab‚Äôs arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim‚Äôs family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?
